query:
SELECT 
  e.id as environment_id,
  e.name as environment_name,
  ii.id as inspection_item_id,
  CASE WHEN ii.id IS NULL THEN 'SEM ITEM' ELSE 'TEM ITEM' END as status
FROM environments e
LEFT JOIN inspection_items ii ON e.id = ii.environment_id
WHERE e.project_id = 1
ORDER BY e.name;
